example_explanations.issuesFound: Count of issues found in the codebase (integer). Example: 2 issues found during your implementation
example_explanations.issuesFixed: Count of issues fixed in the codebase (integer). Example: 1 issue fixed during your implementation
example_explanations.fixAttempts: Count of distinct implementation attempts before success (integer). Example: 2 retries = 3 attempts during your implementation
